::Hurricane was created by Cicadacon of the Tripredacus Council, but he soon 
rebelled and escaped from the lab, killing everyone in his path.  When he 
heard about the Neo Beast Wars he took a pod to past earth.  He got the beast 
mode of a bull.  He than walked up to the Alliance base::
Hurricane: Alliance! I wish to join up with you as a mercenary!
